                    One number
                  </li>
                  <li className={`flex items-center ${/[!@#$%^&*(),.?":{}|<>]/.test(password) ? 'text-green-600' : ''}`}>
                    <div className={`w-2 h-2 rounded-full mr-2 ${/[!@#$%^&*(),.?":{}|<>]/.test(password) ? 'bg-green-500' : 'bg-gray-300'}`}></div>
